data.description: Situated on a corner lot in the conveniently located Oakridge Estates lies this uniquely designed, traditional styled home. This home also sits on a dead end which is adjacent to the driveway and perfect for additional parking for parties, cookouts, and family gatherings. The primary bathroom features a soaker tub, the perfect spot to melt away the stresses of the day, stand alone shower, his and hers vanities, and an ample spaced walk-in closet. Also, featuring beautifully crafted ceilings in the living room and primary bedroom, gorgeous wooden cabinets in the kitchen, and stained concrete floors throughout, this home will not disappoint. Looking for additional storage, man-cave, or she-shed? Look no further than your backyard where an additional 12x20 building awaits to be used however your heart sees fit. The entire inside of the home was painted in 2022, along with replacement of all insulation in the attic and newly installed HVAC system. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer to ramin with home. Step inside, stay awhile, and fall in love. Schedule your showing today!
